# AgentFS — Cursor Agent Instructions

Read AGENTS.md in this repository root for full project context, architecture rules, and development guidelines.

## Quick Reference

- TypeScript strict mode, ESM (`"type": "module"`, `.js` extensions in imports)
- Node.js >= 18.0.0
- `npm run build` to compile, `npm test` to run 261+ Jest tests
- Architecture source of truth: `docs/architecture.md`
- Everything is a file. No databases, no APIs, no cloud dependencies.
- Compile, don't symlink. Idempotent operations only.
- Follow existing formats from architecture doc exactly. Don't invent new conventions.
